    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Song Tracker</h1>
        <p>Song Tracker is a web application designed to help musicians keep track of songs they want to learn and play on their musical instruments.</p>
        
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Track songs you want to play next</li>
            <li>Create and manage your profile</li>
            <li>Search for artists, songs, and albums</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Simply register for an account and start adding songs to your profile. You can organize your music for practice and never forget which songs you wanted to learn.</p>
        
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p><a href="/Register">Register</a> for a new account or <a href="/Login">log in</a> if you already have one and start tracking music.</p>
    </div>
